---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Editorial Policy"
  description="How MyTripTip creates, reviews, and updates its Korea travel guides."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 prose prose-slate">
    <h1>Editorial Policy</h1>

    <h2>Our Standards</h2>
    <p>
      Every guide on MyTripTip is written to help first-time visitors to Korea make
      a specific decision. We prioritize accuracy, usefulness, and honesty over volume.
    </p>

    <h2>How We Research</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>We cross-reference official sources, booking platforms, and local Korean-language resources.</li>
      <li>We compare real pricing, availability, and user reviews across multiple platforms.</li>
      <li>We update guides when information changes — every guide shows its last update date.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Affiliate Independence</h2>
    <p>
      We use affiliate links to earn revenue, but affiliate partnerships never determine
      our recommendations. If a non-affiliate option is better for the reader, we recommend it.
      We clearly label all affiliate links and maintain a full
      <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/">Affiliate Disclosure</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Corrections</h2>
    <p>
      If you spot an error or outdated information, please <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.
      We take corrections seriously and update guides promptly.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
